I"ˆ<p>Change target / mode:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl isolate &amp;lt;target&amp;gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Find default mode:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl get-default
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Set a default mode:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl set-default &amp;lt;target&amp;gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Note the <target> needs to end in &#8220;.target&#8221; ie:</target></p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl set-default multi-user.target
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Locations:</p>

<p>/etc/systemd/system</p>

<p>/usr/lib/systemd/system</p>
